                     <interp inst="t18111030-78-verdict428" type="verdictSubcategory" value="lesserOffence"></interp>
               Of stealing, but not of the burglary
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t18111030-78-punish429" type="punishmentDescription">
